These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, iced-tea
City: venice, miami
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, taxi
1. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Beverage   | iced-tea    | tea |
| City         | miami | venice    |
| Transport     | roller     | taxi      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
City: rome, paris
There 2 different types of food: peas, radish
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
2. the person eating peas is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| City      | paris  | rome   |
| Food   | radish | peas  |
| Transport     | train   | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, tulip
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: fantasy, martial-arts
The people use 2 different means of transport: motorbike, ship
1. the person who growstulip is in an even position##4
2. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Flower         | marigold   | tulip  |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | fantasy  |
| Transport         | motorbike   | ship |

