1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday         | april    | march    |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary     | martial-arts      |
| Sport         | basketball | water-polo |

