.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, radish
There are 2 different nationalities: brazilian, american
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the brazilian##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk##3
3. the person eating pepper is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | radish | pepper     |
| Nationality     | american | brazilian |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | juice    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-8::.
