2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, baccarat
1. the fonseca-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |     2      |
| Flower   | lily | azalea       |
| Hobby      | traveling     | skydiving  |
| Cigar        | baccarat          | fonseca |

